    "input": "input_json is raw JSON SOURCE TEXT. Consumers MUST json-parse it with their standard parser, then hash the parsed value \u2014 this mirrors the \u00a73.2 wire path (bytes -> parse -> hash) and is the ONLY representation that can carry the must-reject inputs (NaN, lone surrogates, over-depth, over-cap integers).",
